Last Updated; May 22, 2014

At Michigan ... U-M Athletic Academic Achievement Award winner (2014).

Freshman (2014) ... Outdoor ... Redshirted ... Indoor ... Redshirted.

Prep ... Graduated from Forest Hills Eastern (2013) ... National Honor Society ... Honor Roll ... AP Scholar ... Track & Field ... MHSAA state champion in 300m hurdles (2013) ... Set school record in 300m hurdles (38.05) and 110m hurdles (15.00) (2013) ... MHSAA All-Academic (2013) ... Member of fifth-place 4x100m relay at MHSAA state meet (2013) ... Took fourth in 300m hurdles at Midwest Meet of Champions (2013) ... Named to West Michigan Dream Team (2013) ... Three-time MHSAA D2 All-State (2012, '13 (2)) ... Two-time OK Bronze All-Conference (2012, '13) ... Two-time member of OK Bronze Conference championship team (2012, '13).

Personal ... Enrolled in College of Literature, Science and the Arts ... Undeclared major ... Born May 27, 1995 ... Son of Steve and Donna Robbins ... Other Sports Played ... Participated in soccer ... Two-time All-Conference (2012, '13).
